text:
While the contested ring has the Void element, the current conflict is considered to be a Void conflict (in addition to any other elements of the contested ring).

- [Isawa Atsuko](https://fiveringsdb.com/card/isawa-atsuko)'s ability can be used. 

- [Keeper of Void](https://fiveringsdb.com/card/keeper-of-void) can be triggered after you win the conflict on defense;

- Void ring effect can be resolved whenever a player resolves the ring effect (including via card abilities);

- [Keeper Initiate](https://fiveringsdb.com/card/keeper-initiate) and [Seeker Initiate](https://fiveringsdb.com/card/seeker-initiate) can be triggered after you claim a ring that gained the Void element via Isawa Kaede.

While the contested ring has the Air element, the current conflict is considered to be an Air conflict (in addition to any other elements of the contested ring):

- [Fearsome Mystic](https://fiveringsdb.com/card/fearsome-mystic) gets her glory bonus;

- [Keeper of Air](https://fiveringsdb.com/card/keeper-of-air) can be triggered after you win the conflict on defense;

- Air ring effect can be resolved whenever a player resolves the ring effect (including via card abilities);

- [Keeper Initiate](https://fiveringsdb.com/card/keeper-initiate) and [Seeker Initiate](https://fiveringsdb.com/card/seeker-initiate) can be triggered after you claim a ring that gained the Air element via Seeker of Knowledge.

Embrace the Void can be triggered any time fate is removed from attached character:
- During the Fate phase;
- Due to the Void ring effect;
- Due to a card ability that says "remove" ([Meditations on the Tao](https://fiveringsdb.com/card/meditations-on-the-tao)), "return" ([Jade Tetsubō](https://fiveringsdb.com/card/jade-tetsubo)), or "move" ([Togashi Kazue](https://fiveringsdb.com/card/togashi-kazue)) fate;
- When attached character leaves play (e.g. [Assassinated](https://fiveringsdb.com/card/assassination)).
